meanings.definition: Not able to be analyzed or broken down further.
meanings.sent1: The ancient artifact was unanalyzable, leaving archaeologists puzzled.
meanings.sent2: The complex equation was unanalyzable for the students.
meanings.sent3: The unanalyzable situation made everyone scratch their heads in confusion.
meanings.sent4: Her emotions were an unanalyzable mix of joy and sadness.
meanings.sent5: The unanalyzable painting left art critics speechless.

meanings.definition: Incapable of being understood or explained.
meanings.sent1: The foreign language was unanalyzable to the tourists.
meanings.sent2: The mysterious phenomenon was unanalyzable by science.
meanings.sent3: His unanalyzable behavior always kept his friends guessing.
meanings.sent4: The unanalyzable truth finally came to light.
meanings.sent5: The unanalyzable dream haunted her all night.
